Dinner @sorelle_chs 🍷🍝

“Southern Italy meets  Southern hospitality at Sorelle, a dining destination like no other on Charleston’s storied Broad Street. 

Inspired by Italy’s all-day cafes, abundant markets and rich culinary traditions, Sorelle features a mercato, central bar, wine room, and a grand dining room offering a variety of experiences for every food lover.” The perfect date night spot! 🍷

Boone Hall Pumpkin Patch 🎃🍂

Fall is here in Charleston and one of my favorite ways to celebrate is to head to @boonehallfarm ! From the hay ride to the pumpkin patch, there is something for everyone of all ages. Open Friday-Sunday 🎃

📍Located 2434 N Hwy 17, Mt Pleasant, SC

Admission Includes:
• Halloween Tractor Tour
• 8-Acre Corn Maze
• Petting Zoo
• Pig Races
• Comedy Circus
• Two of SC’s Largest Jump Pillows
• Inflatable Giant Slide and Obstacle Course
•Swings, Spiders, and Slides
• Live Interactive Honeybee Exhibit
• Rubber Duck Races
• Farm Football
• Stage Live Performances

The Pumpkin Patch at Mistletoe Lane 🎃

📍 Located on 3408 Mistletoe Lane Summerville, SC

“Located in Summerville, The Pumpkin Patch at Mistletoe Lane is described as a “down-home, unique experience.” This pumpkin patch seems to have it all: Straw bales, kettle corn, cider, gourds, pumpkins, firewood, and seasonal flowers! Live music is offered on the weekends starting at noon.” 

Open: Tuesday-Sunday

Introducing @thepalmsocial_ 🌴🤳🏽🎥

Our mission is to elevate your brand through the power of compelling content. With commitment to quality, innovation, and an eye for detail, we take pride in delivering top quality content that resonates with and captivates your audience. We are a team of creative minds driven by a shared vision: to transform your ideas into striking and impactful content.

Whether you are a small business looking to establish your online presence or an established brand seeking a fresh perspective, Palm Social is your partner in bringing your creative vision to life.

Introducing @thepalmsocial_ 🌴🤳🏽

I am excited to announce my latest project of being the Co-Founder & Lead Media Strategist at Palm Social. I started posting on social media as a creative outlet during my senior year in college and never expected to be working full time in social media. After a few years of taking a chance on myself and becoming a content creator for my personal brand and clients in the Lowcountry, I realized it was time to branch out, and founded Palm Social. I have been overwhelmed with opportunities in Charleston and getting to travel for social media in the past few years. I could not be more thankful! I’m very proud to present, Palm Social. We are now accepting new clients for 2024! 🫶🏼
